Start Pip
	python -m ensurepip
Installing Packages
	pip install <package_name>
	pip install <package_name>==1.0.4
	pip install <package_name> >= 1.0.4
	pip install --trusted-host <host_name> -i <host_name> <package_name>(or use pip 1.5.6 to avoid it)

Requirements Files
	pip install -r requirements.txt 
	pip freeze > requirements.txt (use to hold the result from pip freeze -> repeatable installations)

Constrains Files (Requirements files that only control version)
	pip install -c constrains.txt

Uninstalling Packages
	pip uninstall <package_name>

Listing Packages
	pip list
